<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drink-n">drink <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /drɪŋk/    美 /drɪŋk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] (一份或一杯) 饮料；酒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a cold / hot drink
冷/热饮</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go for a drink
去喝一杯</p></div>

